            <title>联想推出 2023 款 ThinkPad S2 Yoga 笔记本电脑：360 度翻转触控屏、100% sRGB 色域，5799 元起</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/740/488.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/740/488.htm</guid>
