            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
                    <div class="tougao-user">感谢IT之家网友 <a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1790356" rel="nofollow">很宅很怕生</a> 的线索投递！</div>
            <p><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT之家</a> 12 月 20 日消息，联想今天在电商平台上架了 2023&nbsp;款&nbsp;ThinkPad S2 Yoga&nbsp;笔记本电脑，主打&nbsp;100% sRGB&nbsp;色域、360 度翻转触控屏，拥有两种处理器版本可选，IT之家整理价格如下：</p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p><span class="accentTextColor">AMD&nbsp;锐龙&nbsp;R5-7530U Pro&nbsp;处理器 + 16G RAM + 512G SSD</span>：售&nbsp;5799&nbsp;元</p></li><li><p><span class="accentTextColor">英特尔酷睿&nbsp;i5-1335U&nbsp;处理器 + 16G RAM + 512G SSD</span>：售&nbsp;6999&nbsp;元</p></li><li><p><span class="accentTextColor">英特尔酷睿&nbsp;i7-1355U&nbsp;处理器 + 32G RAM + 1TB SSD</span>：售&nbsp;8999&nbsp;元</p></li></ul><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="758" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/dd15ea1d-c594-4eb6-a50c-d6d132c84b2b.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想推出 2023 款 ThinkPad S2 Yoga 笔记本电脑：360 度翻转触控屏、100% sRGB 色域，5799 元起" width="432" /></p><p>这款笔记本重量&nbsp;1.26&nbsp;千克、厚度&nbsp;17.23mm，采用&nbsp;13.3&nbsp;英寸 1200P 屏幕，屏幕比例 16:10，分辨率 1920x1200，屏占比&nbsp;82.7%，亮度&nbsp;300&nbsp;尼特<span class="accentTextColor"></span>。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1124" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/a00787a6-1d9c-4255-9c2d-57fe64b7a82d.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想推出 2023 款 ThinkPad S2 Yoga 笔记本电脑：360 度翻转触控屏、100% sRGB 色域，5799 元起" width="628" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1038" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/6cd80131-7352-4db0-9c60-01bf8377c6ae.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想推出 2023 款 ThinkPad S2 Yoga 笔记本电脑：360 度翻转触控屏、100% sRGB 色域，5799 元起" width="610" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1048" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/cfbf5a29-53da-45b5-ade5-122bc436f3a5.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想推出 2023 款 ThinkPad S2 Yoga 笔记本电脑：360 度翻转触控屏、100% sRGB 色域，5799 元起" width="604" /></p><p>此外，联想提到该笔记本拥有“升级版杜比音效”，支持键盘亮度“微亮模式”，拥有指纹识别、物理摄像头挡板及“小红帽经典设计”。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="888" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/1c63d92f-030a-4a26-a80d-47f0af29d2e8.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想推出 2023 款 ThinkPad S2 Yoga 笔记本电脑：360 度翻转触控屏、100% sRGB 色域，5799 元起" width="598" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1056" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/a7d29c7a-ca53-4d46-a174-4cd72344c521.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想推出 2023 款 ThinkPad S2 Yoga 笔记本电脑：360 度翻转触控屏、100% sRGB 色域，5799 元起" width="628" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="1082" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/d9be25d1-7c3c-41d1-a0dc-8818afb908ab.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想推出 2023 款 ThinkPad S2 Yoga 笔记本电脑：360 度翻转触控屏、100% sRGB 色域，5799 元起" width="620" /></p><p>续航方面，这款笔记本配备 46Whr 容量电池，<span class="accentTextColor">号称休眠待机续航&nbsp;12.2&nbsp;小时、节能办公可用&nbsp;8.8&nbsp;小时</span>。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="422" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/77204e62-d102-4568-a0d5-d218f6288368.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想推出 2023 款 ThinkPad S2 Yoga 笔记本电脑：360 度翻转触控屏、100% sRGB 色域，5799 元起" width="610" /></p><p>接口方面，这款笔记本拥有两个&nbsp;USB-A 3.2 Gen 1 接口、一个&nbsp;USB-C&nbsp;接口、一个雷电 4（全功能 USB-C）接口、一个 HDMI 2.0 接口、一个 3.5mm 音频接口。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img height="976" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/3340d880-7ff8-4271-a623-0f3293616c6a.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想推出 2023 款 ThinkPad S2 Yoga 笔记本电脑：360 度翻转触控屏、100% sRGB 色域，5799 元起" width="628" /></p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/EznCl8v" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/e580ce3c-70b1-4af4-8e9f-17e0737f0fc6.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想推出 2023 款 ThinkPad S2 Yoga 笔记本电脑：360 度翻转触控屏、100% sRGB 色域，5799 元起" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name"> ThinkPad S2 Yoga 2023 笔记本</span></span><span class="card-abstract">“AMD R5-7530U Pro + 16G + 512G”款</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 5799 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/E8nzU6L" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/4ac530ad-303c-40ab-a7e8-90623fdcea6e.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想推出 2023 款 ThinkPad S2 Yoga 笔记本电脑：360 度翻转触控屏、100% sRGB 色域，5799 元起" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name"> ThinkPad S2 Yoga 2023 笔记本</span></span><span class="card-abstract">“英特尔酷睿 i5-1335U + 16G + 512G 款”</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price">6999 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://u.jd.com/EsnO87K" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/7a4fda88-15ca-47e9-9ff4-2d0f7cc2f34a.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="联想推出 2023 款 ThinkPad S2 Yoga 笔记本电脑：360 度翻转触控屏、100% sRGB 色域，5799 元起" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name"> ThinkPad S2 Yoga 2023 笔记本</span></span><span class="card-abstract">“英特尔酷睿 i7-1355U + 32G + 1TB”款</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 8999 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时间，结果仅供参考，IT之家所有文章均包含本声明。</p>
